      <title>印度卢比看涨头寸达到两年多高位；路透调查：亚洲外汇空头坚守阵地</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/bullish-positions-indian-rupee-over-two-year-high-asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透周四的一项调查显示，由于中国经济复苏的不确定性和全球货币宽松时间表拖延，印度卢比的看涨押注达到两年半以来的最高水平，而投资者对大多数亚洲货币维持看跌头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/bullish-positions-indian-rupee-over-two-year-high-asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-2024-03-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:47:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
